 📈 Sentimental Drive

AI-Powered Sentiment-Driven Stock Prediction System for NIFTY 100


## 🌟 Features

- **📊 Live Market Dashboard** — Real-time NIFTY 50, NIFTY 100, BANKNIFTY, SENSEX via Angel One SmartAPI WebSocket
- **🤖 AI Prediction Engine** — XGBoost model trained on 138,000+ rows across 100 NIFTY stocks
- **📰 Sentiment Analysis** — VADER NLP scoring on live headlines from NewsAPI and Google News
- **🔍 Stock Screener** — Filter 100 stocks by sector, signal, RSI range, and sentiment score simultaneously
- **📈 Interactive Charts** — Candlestick and line charts with SMA 50/200 overlays and 5 time ranges
- **🎯 BUY/SELL/HOLD Signals** — ML prediction + technical confirmation rules (RSI, MACD, SMA)
- **⚡ 6-Tab Stock Detail** — Summary, Chart, Analysis, Sentiment, AI Prediction, Peers
- **🔄 Auto Fallback** — Angel One → yfinance fallback so the app always works
- **💾 Smart Caching** — TTL-based Redis-ready cache for fast repeated requests
- **📱 Responsive Dark UI** — Institutional-grade dark theme built with Tailwind CSS

---

## 🏗️ System Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                        DATA SOURCES                              │
│   yfinance (historical) │ Angel One SmartAPI │ NewsAPI │ Google  │
└────────────┬────────────┴─────────┬──────────┴────┬────────────┘
             │                      │               │
             ▼                      ▼               ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                     PROCESSING LAYER                             │
│   Feature Engineering (22 features) │ VADER Sentiment Scoring   │
└────────────────────────┬────────────┴────────────────────────────┘
                         │
                         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      ML ENGINE                                   │
│   XGBoost Classifier │ Random Forest │ Heuristic Fallback        │
└────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────┘
                         │
                         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    FASTAPI BACKEND                               │
│   REST API (4 endpoints) │ WebSocket /ws/market │ TTL Cache      │
└────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────┘
                         │
                         ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                  REACT FRONTEND                                  │
│   Stock Screener │ 6-Tab Detail │ Live Ticker │ Candlestick      │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Frontend** | React 18 + Vite | SPA dashboard |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | Dark theme UI |
| **State** | TanStack Query | Server state + 5min cache |
| **Charts** | Recharts | Line, area, bar charts |
| **Backend** | FastAPI + Uvicorn | REST API + WebSocket server |
| **ML Model** | XGBoost, scikit-learn, LightGBM | Stock direction prediction |
| **NLP** | VADER Sentiment | News headline scoring |
| **Indicators** | TA library | RSI, MACD, BB, ATR (22 features) |
| **Live Data** | Angel One SmartAPI | Real-time prices + WebSocket stream |
| **Historical** | yfinance | 5yr OHLCV data per stock |
| **News** | NewsAPI + Google News | Headlines for sentiment |
| **Auth** | pyotp (TOTP 2FA) | Angel One session management |
| **Serialization** | joblib | Model .pkl save/load |

