## 🔌 API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/` | Health check |
| `GET` | `/api/bootstrap` | Load market + all stocks in one call |
| `GET` | `/api/market` | Live NIFTY indices data |
| `GET` | `/api/stocks` | All 100 NIFTY stocks with signals |
| `GET` | `/api/stocks/{symbol}` | Full stock detail with prediction |
| `GET` | `/api/top-picks` | Top BUY and SELL signals |
| `WS` | `/ws/market` | Live market WebSocket stream |

### Example response — `/api/stocks/RELIANCE`

```json
{
  "symbol": "RELIANCE",
  "company_name": "Reliance Industries Ltd",
  "sector": "Energy",
  "current_price": 2847.50,
  "change_pct": 1.23,
  "rsi": 58.4,
  "macd": 12.3,
  "sentiment_score": 0.42,
  "signal": "BUY",
  "prediction": "UP",
  "confidence": 62.0,
  "history": [...],
  "news": [...],
  "feature_importance": [...]
}
```

